observer group attached to the U.N. Interim Force in Lebanon, Feb.
17, 1988. Kidnapped near Tyre. Claimed by the pro-Iranian
Organization of the Oppressed on Earth, a Shiite faction. The group
said April 21, 1988 that Higgins would be put on trial for spying.
